	<description><![CDATA[ 
<h1>Joomla Web Developer Tools</h1>
			<p>Some Web Develpment tools to make your life easier when editing Joomla!</p>
			<ul>
				<li>CSS Refresh</li>
				<li>W3C Code Checker</li>
			</ul>
			<p>Check out more at <a href="http://www.cecilomar.com/projects/webdevjools/" target="_blank">http://www.cecilomar.com/projects/webdevjools/</a></p>
